platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With its unique take on world domination, Sid Meier’s Civilization has captured gamers’ imaginations for more than 20 years. Civilization Revolution 2 carries the franchise’s winning formula to iPhone and iPad, expanding on its predecessor with a new arsenal of troops, technologies, and characters. Complex tactics and gorgeous 3D design make each match a pleasure as players expand their empire, make allies, and declare war using famous leaders ranging from Napoleon to JFK.
